  <entry>
    <title>【学习笔记】配对堆学习笔记</title>
    <link href="https://leverimmy.top/2020/03/16/%E3%80%90%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0%E3%80%91%E9%85%8D%E5%AF%B9%E5%A0%86%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/"/>
    <id>https://leverimmy.top/2020/03/16/%E3%80%90%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0%E3%80%91%E9%85%8D%E5%AF%B9%E5%A0%86%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/</id>
    <published>2020-03-16T03:51:46.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-05-06T04:05:42.000Z</updated>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;配对堆是一种 &lt;strong&gt;被猜想&lt;/strong&gt; 能均摊 $O(\log n)$ 删除，其余 &lt;strong&gt;所有&lt;/strong&gt; 操作（包括但不限于 $\text{top}, \text{make-heap}, \text{decrease-key}, \text{meld}$ 等）均摊 $O(1)$ 的数据结构。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.cs.cmu.edu/afs/cs.cmu.edu/user/sleator/www/papers/pairing-heaps.pdf&quot;&gt;pdf 论文&lt;/a&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
